dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Topographic maps of Karafuto Prefecture, South Sakhalin.
Index to adjoining sheets in margins.
Each map individually numbered and titled at top margin by place name.
reprinted Feb. 1947 by Kyodo Printing Co. Ltd.
